This modern mixed use development occupies a high profile location between Ellen Stirling Boulevard and the Cedric Street off-ramp, within close proximity to Stirling Train Station and excellent retail amenity.

The key features of this offering include:

- Modern tenancies with flexible areas on offer;

- High profile location with signage rights available;

- Low estimated outgoings of $54.02/sqm for the 2019/20 
financial year.

- Excellent Parking Availability.

The following tenancies are available immediately:

Level 1 Office - 491.6qm. Partitioned tenancy featuring polished concrete floors and excellent natural light, incorporating a reception/waiting area, boardroom, 3 x offices/meeting rooms, large kitchen/breakout, open plan working area and comms. The tenancy is ready for occupation with cabling, access control and alarm system installed.

Ground Floor - Retail - 130sqm. Positioned opposite the entrance to IKEA, this tenancy has access via Sunray Drive and the car parking area. Great opportunity for a multitude of uses.

Shower facilities are provided within the building.


For further information, or to arrange an inspection, please contact the leasing agents.

Office - Rick McKenzie or James Phelan
Retail - Joe Bergic.

•Air conditioned

Introducing 'The Garden Office Park', a unique A Grade office offering only 10 mins from the Perth CBD. 

What makes Garden Office Park so unique is the vast amount of tenant amenity available to the modern office worker at affordable market rates. This includes; 

- Secure private and public car parking. Ratio 1:30sqm
- Beautiful activated landscaped gardens
- Onsite bar, restaurant & cafe
- New end of trip facilities
- Gym, tennis court & swimming pool
- Conference Facilities 
- Onsite building management, security & 24hour helpdesk
- Glendalough train within 400m
- CAT bus services in close proximity 

The owner takes great pride in this complex with a focus on the health and well-being of all their customers. Tenant retention and occupancy levels far exceed the market norm.
